## Development Workflow

### Adding an Endpoint

1. Add route in `app/api/v1/endpoints.py`
2. Add schema in `app/schemas/`
3. Add service in `app/services/`
{% if include_tests %}4. Write tests{% endif +%}
5. Update docs

